@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p class="text-muted">Last updated: April 2026</p>

<hr />

<h5>Data We Store</h5>
<p>TaskFlow stores only the task data you create: titles, descriptions, due dates, priorities, and categories. All data is saved locally in a SQLite database on the server.</p>

<h5>Data We Do Not Collect</h5>
<p>We do not collect personal information, track usage analytics, or share any data with third parties.</p>

<h5>Cookies</h5>
<p>TaskFlow uses only essential session cookies required for form security (anti-forgery tokens). No tracking or advertising cookies are used.</p>

<h5>Your Data</h5>
<p>You can delete any task or category at any time directly from the app. No data is retained after deletion.</p>

<h5>Contact</h5>
<p>If you have any questions about this policy, please reach out via the project repository.</p>
